Opinion
Pee Cueiam,
Appeal quashed. Cf. Commonwealth ex rel. Austin v. Hendrick, 440 Pa. 236, 269 A. 2d 750 (1970), and Commonwealth ex rel. Gordy v. Lyons, 434 Pa. 165, 252 A. 2d 197 (1969).
Mr. Justice Cohen took no part in the decision of this case.
Mr. Justice Bobeets took no part in the consideration or decision of this case.
